snippet.textDisplay: Babul supriyo deserves more than what he is today. He is nobody king. His voice is so melodious. After certain phase he almost disappeared from musical mainstream,, better than member of parliament he is a singer, whose voice after 7days narayan is the most melodious in Indian musical industries. Nowadays only high pitch song are composed, and have almost forgotten the term melody. High pitch songs are also good but it has never explored outside the domain of Bharatbarsa Fateh Ali Khan.  Our music composer should think about it. Still today pehla song makes our hear and soul exhilarated... Babul da types or melody songs have to be composed...
